Comment: 0,0:03:36.53,0:03:45.54,Title,,0,0,0,,Angel Island Obliterated! \NThe Horror of the Raigo's Advent!!
Comment: 0,0:23:32.60,0:23:36.02,Title,,0,0,0,,Knock Over Giant Jack! \NLast Hope for Escape
