Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.18,0:01:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eneru's attacks mercilessly \Nrained down on all of Skypiea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.68,0:01:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is an eyesore!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.84,0:02:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The people, the trees, the land! \NReturn to where you belong!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.02,0:02:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let everything rain into the Blue Sea!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.20,0:02:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.37,0:02:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel Island won't last much longer!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.79,0:02:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are no safe havens left on this island!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.34,0:02:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Robin and Usopp's \Ngroup was still beneath Giant Jack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.43,0:02:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He's far above now.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.89,0:02:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time until \Nhis ship reaches the top of the vine.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.64,0:02:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it Eneru wants there?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.60,0:02:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A gold bell at the top.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.00,0:02:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A bell...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.82,0:02:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no need for good old God's Shrine either!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.20,0:02:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor for the city of Shandora below it!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.17,0:03:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There is but one thing left \Nin this land that I want!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.71,0:03:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The golden grand belfry!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.38,0:03:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And Luffy, in an attempt to catch Eneru, \Nrushed up Giant Jack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.60,0:03:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami! Be all right!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.77,0:03:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And I won't let you have the golden bell, Eneru!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.34,0:03:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A gold bell?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.34,0:04:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you said?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.93,0:04:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wyper...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.01,0:04:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.64,0:04:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What're you guys talking about?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.69,0:04:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You also spoke of the bell before \Nbeing hit by Eneru's electric attack.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.66,0:04:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's going after it?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.27,0:04:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Where exactly is it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.18,0:04:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait! This is no time for that! \NYou saw that thunderbolt!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.44,0:04:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna die if we don't get outta here!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.54,0:04:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere near the top of this giant vine...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.63,0:04:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How?! How do you know that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.17,0:04:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! We promised we'd wait \Nfor Nami back on our ship!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.93,0:04:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gonna be back with Luffy any time now!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.53,0:04:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right, Wyper!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.27,0:04:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The ruins of Shandora in the layer below us...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.29,0:04:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This vine pierces right through \Nthe very center of the city.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.61,0:04:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez! Look!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.14,0:05:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno if it's ruins or what, \Nbut it's been blasted to pieces!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.12,0:05:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We could be next, you know!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.74,0:05:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A map I found in the ruins \Nindicated that the grand belfry
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.18,0:05:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that held the golden bell was \Nlocated in the city's center.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.30,0:05:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you completely ignoring me?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.97,0:05:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, the shock from \Nbeing thrust upward by the vine
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.26,0:05:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,might have thrown the bell even further skyward.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.52,0:05:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's directly above here?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.40,0:05:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The singing voice of the island...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.16,0:05:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.87,0:05:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The city of gold has a huge bell, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.38,0:06:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then. I'm above Giant Jack.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.35,0:06:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt anyone would come \Nsearching for something
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.47,0:06:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,in these skies above God's Shrine.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.56,0:06:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after 400 years...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.52,0:06:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then. Where is the golden bell...?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.26,0:06:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.68,0:06:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Him...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.35,0:06:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm astonished he made it here \Nwith that weight attached.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.36,0:07:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.82,0:07:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait right there! Eneru!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.57,0:07:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a pest.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.31,0:07:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wyper! What are you planning to do?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.73,0:07:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're gonna climb the vine?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.98,0:07:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! Get away from the vine!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.49,0:07:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's falling!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.25,0:07:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The tip of the vine?! What happened above?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.83,0:08:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now! \NDon't tell me Luffy and Nami fell with it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.40,0:08:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wyper!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.63,0:08:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You can't in your condition! \NYou're all beat up!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.97,0:08:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And even if you do climb up, \Nthere's no way to reach Eneru in the sky!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.06,0:08:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.02,0:08:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's directly above!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.60,0:08:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The bell that Great Warrior Calgara sought!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.53,0:08:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Calgara?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.65,0:08:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.82,0:08:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what our {\i1}true{\i0} goal is!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.58,0:08:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Eneru! I refuse to let you have it!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.39,0:08:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you intend to \Nclimb up here in that state?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.64,0:08:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Damn you!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.36,0:09:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay there for a while. \NI'll show you something interesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.01,0:09:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.14,0:09:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right! \NI gotta figure something out while he's gone!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.61,0:09:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my only choice!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.20,0:10:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.42,0:10:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...Yo-Yo!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.76,0:10:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.56,0:10:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I'm back on track!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.57,0:10:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's my chance to get on board!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.15,0:10:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! I finally caught up to you!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.15,0:10:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Nami! What're {\i1}you{\i0} doing here?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.99,0:10:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to get {\i1}you{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.28,0:10:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji-{\i1}kun{\i0} and Usopp saved me, \Nso I was down below!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.25,0:10:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?! You were?! That's great!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.29,0:10:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But more importantly...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.50,0:10:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.67,0:10:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.22,0:11:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The thunderclouds... are changing shape!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.39,0:11:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.72,0:11:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.73,0:11:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad! Save us!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.19,0:11:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky's pitch dark!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.40,0:11:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.28,0:11:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.23,0:11:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Into the ocean! Quickly!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.28,0:11:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a giant ball floating in the sky!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.37,0:11:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing's bad news...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.71,0:11:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a thundercloud wrapped in a spherical shroud...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.17,0:11:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...and it's packed with intense currents \Nand internal electric discharges!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.77,0:11:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's directly above Angel Island!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.94,0:11:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The thunderclouds turned spherical...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.03,0:12:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,T-This is a nightmare! \NThis isn't something you see in real life!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.74,0:12:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What more is he planning to unleash?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.06,0:12:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Into the ocean!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.99,0:12:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.41,0:12:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you will learn that the heavens are mine!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.95,0:12:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,With the Maxim and my power, \NI can accomplish such acts of God!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.34,0:12:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.55,0:12:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's falling onto Angel Island!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.01,0:13:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.10,0:13:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not going to make it!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.10,0:13:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! Hurry!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.56,0:13:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.69,0:13:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Raigo.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.81,0:13:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this can't be!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.97,0:13:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the White Berets manage to escape?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.40,0:13:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Berets saved us...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.48,0:14:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The island we were born on and our \Nhometown are completely gone!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.17,0:14:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the Sea Clouds were obliterated!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.14,0:14:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What a wonderful sight!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.81,0:14:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This{\i0} is how the sky should be!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.36,0:14:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What {\i1}was{\i0} that explosion?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.73,0:14:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And the thunderbolts are still raining down?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.78,0:14:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get the feeling I'll be leaving alive now!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.11,0:14:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He eradicated Angel Island...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.54,0:15:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be so ruthless, Eneru?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.68,0:15:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What loud rumbling...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.44,0:15:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to wait. \NWe {\i1}have{\i0} to take them back to the Blue Sea!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.82,0:15:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Get on, so we can go back down!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.98,0:15:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's headed for our ship! \NWe gotta get going, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.62,0:15:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.91,0:15:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't? Why not?! \NWhat're you talking about?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.00,0:15:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I don't have to save you now...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.75,0:15:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...I still have unfinished business here!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.46,0:15:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfinished business? \NWhat could you possibly have left to do here?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.44,0:15:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to get back \Nat Eneru or something?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.17,0:15:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a gold bell up above!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.48,0:15:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold? Your life is more important, you know! \NJust look!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.17,0:15:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if lightning doesn't hurt you,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.48,0:16:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,he has the power to destroy \Neverything in other ways!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.94,0:16:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's gold you want, then look! \NYou have some on your arm!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.44,0:16:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about some gold bell! You'll be killed!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.16,0:16:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't die...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.89,0:16:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you quit it, already?! You—
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.95,0:16:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw it yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.46,0:16:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Saw what?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.80,0:16:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The city of gold... it existed!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.18,0:16:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a lie.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.73,0:16:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Old diamond-head's ancestor...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.40,0:16:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If it exists, that's fine. If not, that's fine, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.98,0:16:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not really out to prove \Nhis innocence or anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.49,0:16:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a duel with the man \Nwho screwed up my life.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.75,0:16:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He {\i1}wasn't{\i0} lying.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.21,0:17:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So I have to let the old guy \Nand the others below know...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.42,0:17:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...that the city of gold was in the sky!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.51,0:17:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If I ring the bell... \Nthey should be able to hear it!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.27,0:17:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, they'll keep on searching \Nthe ocean floor until they die!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.86,0:17:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.28,0:17:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let Eneru take it!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.37,0:17:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the huge bell can \Nbe heard from anywhere...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.54,0:17:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...so that's why I'm going to ring the gold bell!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.59,0:17:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! The City of Gold has a huge bell, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.80,0:17:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Noland's logbook did mention it had one.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.10,0:18:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.01,0:18:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.31,0:18:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought up a good idea!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.73,0:18:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What is it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.94,0:18:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If we rang that huge bell,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.17,0:18:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,do you think old diamond-head and the monkeys below would hear it?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.29,0:18:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd hear it, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.08,0:18:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When he says he's gonna \Ndo something, he means it.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.63,0:18:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, he's...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.96,0:18:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He {\i1}did{\i0} say that. But given the situation...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.22,0:18:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to ring the bell, you say?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.69,0:18:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Even if Nami tries to \Nbring him back, he won't come.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.27,0:18:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he's after the same thing Eneru is.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.79,0:19:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.97,0:19:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Who gave you permission to board this ship?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.35,0:19:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Eneru!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.69,0:19:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.71,0:19:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,See! I told you it was a bad idea!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.90,0:19:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn him!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.74,0:19:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Did you see the silly little island vanish from the sky?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.70,0:19:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Girl. I assume you're not \Ngoing to try and sweet-talk me
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.16,0:19:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,by asking me to take you \Nto Endless Vearth again...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.93,0:19:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell, no!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.88,0:19:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I have what I want,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.92,0:19:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I will destroy {\i1}all{\i0} of Skypiea with this next Raigo!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.32,0:20:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can be allowed to escape now!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.35,0:20:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Including the several unmoving \Nvoices directly below you!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.98,0:20:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Directly below?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.90,0:20:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to eradicate this land \Nthat is out of place in the sky
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.36,0:20:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and change everything back to how it should be!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.74,0:20:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That is my duty as God!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.09,0:20:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.05,0:20:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...have your way!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.60,0:20:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell, rubber man!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.81,0:20:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Look on wistfully and wait until the end arrives!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.24,0:20:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.37,0:21:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.04,0:21:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can stop me now.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.67,0:21:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.47,0:21:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen! \NWe {\i1}will{\i0} send you into the sky, without fail!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.10,0:21:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.86,0:21:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.74,0:21:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...will ring that bell!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:10.99,0:23:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see the power of the Raigo?!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:13.12,0:23:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up are the cumuloregalis clouds themselves!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:15.71,0:23:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there anything we can do?!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:16.75,0:23:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's important that we, the inheritors \Nof Calgara's wishes, ring that bell!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:21.05,0:23:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock over this vine?! \NAm I our last line of defense after all?!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:24.55,0:23:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Guarantee me I'll survive!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:27.43,0:23:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 10,0:23:28.43,0:23:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock Over Giant Jack! \NLast Hope for Escape
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.68,0:23:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
